title: BONUS: Jadakiss & Set Free On The Legacy Of And1 Mixtape, Streetball & 30 For 30
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Jadakiss and Set Free sat down with Ebro in the Morning to discuss the legendary And1 mixtape, mixing hip hop and basketball, how it got started, and much more! 30 For 30's ‘The Greatest Mixtape Ever’ is available now on ESPN+ now! 

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
